(198, 1, '2019-06-25 07:44:08', '2019-06-25 07:44:08', '<span class=\"title2\">THE COVEHILL LADIES</span>\r\n\r\nJennifer became an orphan at a very young age. However, the course of her life is set to change as she becomes an instant millionaire. Her life becomes more exciting as she falls in love with her wild, Irish next-door neighbor. But as time goes by, a huge secret about her past begins to unfold. Is it too late for second chances? Or is this what she has been waiting for her whole life?', 'Sub About the Book 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sub-about-the-book-2', '', '', '2019-06-25 07:44:47', '2019-06-25 07:44:47', '', 11, 'http://mary-ann.local/?page_id=198', 0, 'page', '', 0),
